These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, indonesian, dutch, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, sunflower, zinnia, lily
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person who growsazalea is not to the left of the person who growsazalea##8
 3. the person who growslily is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the person who growsazalea is not to the right of the person who growsazalea##8
 6. the dutch is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the italian is between the person who growssunflower and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person who growslily is the dutch##1
10. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the polish##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the dutch is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who growszinnia##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Nationality   | indonesian | italian   | polish   | dutch  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Flower     | azalea    | zinnia | sunflower     | lily    |

