.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, golf, cricket, water-polo
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bolivar, blend, old-henry
 1. the fan of salsa is between the tiparillo-smoker and the fan of indie##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
 8. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the bolivar-smoker##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
11. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the bolivar-smoker##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Sport          | water-polo     | golf | swimming | cricket  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Cigar           | blend | old-henry | tiparillo    | bolivar  |

