There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the tower house##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
 8. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the ranch-style house is on the left of the modern house##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the tower house is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
12. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | sudoku   | skydiving | card-games |
| House   | tower     | gothic-revival  | ranch-style   | modern      |
