The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rowing, tennis
 1. the person traveling to venice is not the cottage house##6
 2. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person eating plum is the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the cottage house and the cape-cod house##2
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5
 9. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the victorian house##1
10. the cape-cod house is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
14. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
