 9. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
10. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8
11. the electrician is on the far left##1
12. the videographer is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is the craftsman house##1
14. the craftsman house is not to the left of the american##8
15. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the french##5
