 4. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 5. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching sports movies and the fan of salsa##2
 6. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
