.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
House: victorian, colonial, ranch-style, wooden
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
There 4 different types of food: peach, cauliflower, cherry, peas
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the ranch-style house is the person eating peas##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the victorian house is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the colonial house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person eating cauliflower##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
10. the colonial house is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the wooden house##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| House      | victorian   | wooden     | ranch-style    | colonial |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Food         | peach | cherry  | peas     | cauliflower  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

