 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the bartender##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
 4. the teacher is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the social-worker##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the owner of the turtle##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the owner of the mouse is in an even position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
11. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the social-worker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

